captions.text:
- Why hello, everyone!
My name is Tyler Oakley
and before you ask, I cut my finger today.
It's bleeding through the thing.
I cut my finger, it's a long story.

A candle exploded, my
book is all burned up,
and there were embers everywhere.

So I was like, "Oh my God, my
apartment almost burned down."

So I don't know what
candle company this was,

but you have ruined this
book and you are lucky
you did not burn down this apartment,

because I would have sued
or something, I don't know.
So, where was I going with this story?

So, I cut my finger,
that's where I was going.

But we are not here to
talk about my cut finger,

because it is time to open some
shit y'all sent to my PO Box.
Okay, so we have a mug.

Y'all know I love mugs,
but it says @tyleroakley.
So whenever I'm thirsty for some coffee,

I am always more thirsty for
some promo, so thank you.
Okay, so this is a jar.

It says, "Why we love Tyler
Oakley," and it's made by

Lauren and Riley, so thank
you, Lauren and Riley.
I love when people do things like this.
Thank you so much.
This is from G and look at that.

Okay, so this is actually when
I had gray hair, obviously.
But times have changed.

I now have a seafoam,
like a subtle seafoam,

but this is still cute and
lord knows I love a floral,
so thank you.
This says "gay accent mouth spray".
Should we try it? I'm gonna try it.

I don't think I necessarily
have a gay accent.

Although, sometimes people
if they're critiquing me,
like why I'm the worst human in the world,

they say I fake being
gayer than I actually am

just for views or something,
which is ridiculous,

because lord knows if
you have ever met me,

I am exactly how I am in
videos as I am in person.

(coughs)
(laughing)
Oh my God, I was not expecting that.

It sprays a lot wider
than you think it's gonna.
It tastes delicious.
It's like a subtle mint.
I don't think I got any gayer.

I think I'm still expressing
the same amount of gayness
that I usually do, but thank you for that.
Hmm, that's delicious.
Okay, so the next package is something

that I get every month
and it is my NatureBox.
Basically, if you guys don't know,
you can use naturebox.com/tyler to sign up
for snacks delivered to your apartment.

It is super inexpensive
and it's healthy snacks,

like low in trans fats or
low in gluten, or whatever.
It's healthy stuff and basically you pick
whatever size box you want,

it sends those delicious
snacks to your front door,
you don't have to deal with people

and it's kind of the
best thing in the world,
because I hate going grocery shopping
and then it comes straight to my door
and I don't have to even think about it.

This month I am
recommending the whole wheat
figgy blueberry bars.

I think the last few
months I've recommended
all blueberry things.
Maybe I'm on a blueberry kick.

They're high in antioxidants,
so maybe that's why.
You all know I don't talk about something
unless I can give you guys the hookup,
so if you use naturebox.com/tyler
you will get a free box of sample snacks,
so you're welcome in advance.

Oh my God, A to Z Reasons
Why We Love Tyler,
from Kelsey, Elise, and Josie.
Thank you, girls.
Should we see some of the reasons?
Okay, let's see.
B is for Bad Biotch! (laughs)
That's amazing.
D is for Dayyum Boi!

E is for Explosive Diarrhea,
because obviously, my brand.
N is for Nastay.

Oh my God, y'all, and it's got
a little dancing woman Emoji.
I'm kind of obsessed.
You know me.
Okay, so this is from Sophia in New York
and it has a little message.
It says, "Dear Tyler Oakley,
"Hi, my name is Sophia, I'm 13 years old.

"I have been watching your
videos for two years now

"and I am in love with
you, not in a creepy way."
I always appreciate when y'all clarify

that you're not creepy,
because that's necessary.

"Please, please wear this
sweater in one of your videos.
"I hope it's the right size.

"Also, please tell Jack
Scap to make a new video."
(laughing) Oh my God, that's amazing.

Okay, let's see what
the sweater is, Sophia.
Um ...
I feel like I could cry.
Oh my God, Sophia, no.

It is the Born This Way
album cover on a sweater.
Okay, since this is the best gift ever,

I will for sure tell Jack
Scap to make a new video.
Only for you.

Okay, so this is from
Jasmine in Washington
and, Oh my God.
Y'all, what are you trying to do to me?
Ok, first and foremost, my breath is fine.
I don't know why you sent me the gay spray
and now, ranch-flavored mints?
What are y'all trying to tell me?

I swear I have fresh breath,
but a ranch-flavored mint?
Do we want to try that?
Last time was ranch-flavored soda
and that was not cute.
(playful music)

It's exactly what you'd
think it tastes like.
I can't, no. (gagging)
Oh my God, thank you, but no thank you.

Okay, so this next package
obviously looks like a hula hoop.
I'm gonna assume it's hula hoops,
but what's different about it?
Can we? I'm gonna open it.

(bubble wrap popping)
Ooh!

Oh my God, that is just
so satisfying, oh yes.
Yep, yep, uh-huh, oh!
This is from Jess Hoops in Dallas, Texas.
Oh my God, I almost cut your letter.
I see it right there, okay.

Jess Hoops, if that is
your real name, I swear,

that is fate, especially
if you are into hula hoops
as much as I assume you are,
because you're sending me hula hoops.

Okay, it is exactly what I
thought it was, two hula hoops.
Wait, what?
This is a double hula hoop?
(gasps) What is going on?
How big is this hula hoop?

"Hi Tyler. First of all, thank
you so much for your channel.
"You may be wondering why I've sent you
"this huge ass hula hoop.
"My name is Jess and I make adult-sized
"hula hoops for a living.
"The hoops I make are larger and sturdier
"than hula hoops you'd find at the store
"and they're made for adult bodies."

Well, I have a child's
body, but thank you.
I will use this adult hula hoop.
Oh my God! (laughing)

Jess, thank you for
awakening my childhood spirit
and passion for hula hooping.

I will now be leaving YouTube
for a full-time career
in the hoop dance.

Just kidding, I'm not leaving,
but honestly, maybe I ...
(laughing)
Thank you for watching this video.
I think that's all I'm gonna open today.

If you like this video, be
sure to give it a thumbs up

and maybe I won't leave
YouTube for hula hooping.

If you'd like to see my
latest video click right here.

It is 10 things that I do
when I wake up in the morning.

If you want to hear my latest
podcast that came out today.

Click right here, it's with
Korey and it was so fun.

We talked all about celebrity
conspiracy theories,
which was kind of amazing.
We talked all about Larry Stylinson.

If you want to hear about
that, click right there.
Subscribe on iTunes and if you want to be
my Person of the Week, click right there.
You can get a shirt, send me a picture
of you being cute in it and you might be
my Person of the Week.
It's that simple.

If you haven't already
subscribed, we are getting

dangerously close to
6 million subscribers.

So thank you guys for
always being so supportive.
I hope you guys like this video.
If you want me to do more PO Box videos,
let me know in the comments below,
but until next time, have a good life
and I will see you later.
Okay, bye!

(laughing) This is the
most fun I've had all day.
Oh my God, wait, this is--
Hello, this is my new life.
